rows.label: tlk47100012_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Wow. Ever since I came here,
I've had nothing but fun!

rows.label: tlk47100012_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Everyone's been fawning over
me and giving me free food...

rows.label: tlk47100012_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Phonexes are easily pleased.
Give us tasty treats and suddenly,
we're your best friend.

rows.label: tlk47100012_01_msg0004
rows.name:
We have different tastes
depending on our homeland,
though. Just remember that.
